CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1956, pg. A25, reads: "Attended NAACP Rally - The Youth Council of the local branch of the National Association for the Advancement of Colored People held a youth rally last Friday evening at the Centre Avenue YMCA.  Job opportunities and activity in the civil rights fields were discussed.  Among those attending were, left to right: Eloise Patterson, treasurer of the council; the Rev. Leroy Patrick, guest speaker; Billie Smith, secretary, and Ronald Browne, president. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eloise Patterson, Rev. LeRoy Patrick, Billie Smith, and Ronald Browne gathered for NAACP Youth Council rally
